<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">

<head>
  <meta charset="euc-kr">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>NICE지키미</title>

  <script src="../../../js/bzw/jquery-1.11.3.js"></script>
  <script src="../../../js/bzw/jquery-ui.min.js"></script>
  <script src="../../../js/bzw/swiper.min.js"></script> 
  <script src="../../../js/bzw/ui.common.js"></script>

  <link rel="stylesheet" href="../../../css/zkm/bzw/swiper.min.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="../../../css/zkm/bzw/common.css">
</head>

<body>
  <div id="skipNavi">
    <a href="#content">본문내용 바로가기</a>
  </div>
  <div id="wrap">
    <!-- header -->
    <script type="text/javascript" src="../../../bzw/inc/header.js"></script>
    <script type="text/javascript" src="../../../bzw/inc/breadcrumbs.js"></script>
    <!--// header -->

    <!-- container -->
    <div id="container">
      <div id="content">
        <div class="section">
          <a href="#modal" class="btn base modalOpen">소득정보 등록</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <!--// container -->

    <!-- popup -->
    <div class="uiModal full active" id="modal">
      <div class="modalWrap">
        <div class="cookieBox">
          <div class="uiItem">
            <input type="checkbox" name="period" id="today">
            <label for="today"><span>오늘 그만보기</span></label>
          </div>
          <div class="uiItem">
            <input type="checkbox" name="period" id="week">
            <label for="week"><span>1주일 그만보기</span></label>
          </div>
        </div>
        <button type="button" class="uiBtn typeModalClose"><span class="hidden">닫기</span></button>
        <div class="modalHeader">
          <h1>소득정보 등록</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="modalContent">
          <div class="inner">
            <!-- content -->
            <div class="governing">
              <h2 class="governingTitle">
                금융기관이 
                신용카드 발급 심사 등에 활용할 수 있는 
                <strong class="pColor">소득정보를 등록</strong>하는 방법을 알려드려요.
              </h2>
            </div>
            <ol class="listCircle">
              <li>
                <i>1</i>
                <span class="exp">소득금액증명서 조회</span>
                <div class="innerBox">
                  <ol>
                    <li>① 국세청 홈택스 방문 (www.hometax.go.kr)</li>
                    <li>② 소득금액증명서 조회</li>
                    <li>③ 발급번호 확인</li>
                  </ol>
                </div>
              </li>
              <li>
                <i>2</i>
                <span class="exp">발급번호 입력</span>
                <div class="innerBox">
                  <ol>
                    <li>① 간편소득정보 등록신청</li>
                    <li>② 발급번호 입력</li>
                  </ol>
                </div>
              </li>
              <li>
                <i>3</i>
                <span class="exp">담당자 확인 및 등록</span>
                <div class="innerBox">
                  <ul class="listDot">
                    <li>소득증빙서류 확인발급</li>
                    <li>발급번호 입력 시점으로부터 영업일 기준 3~5일 소요</li>
                  </ul>
                </div>
              </li>
              <li>
                <i>4</i>
                <span class="exp">변경완료</span>
                <div class="innerBox">
                  <ul class="listDot">
                    <li>변경완료</li>
                    <li>철회가능 (☎ 1588-2486)</li>
                  </ul>
                </div>
              </li>
            </ol>
            <!--// content -->
          </div>
          <div class="modalBottom">
            <div class="btns">
              <button type="button" class="btn primary"><span>소득정보 등록</span></button>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <!--// popup -->

    <!-- footer -->
    <div class="footer"></div>
    <!--// footer -->
  </div>
</body>

</html>